QuickStroke – FAST Stroke Screening Framework

Copyright 2026 KpunWP / QuickStroke Team

QuickStroke was originally created as an open-source, privacy-first,
browser-based FAST stroke screening framework for preliminary stroke risk
screening using Face, Arm, and Speech modules.

Original project:
https://github.com/KpunWP/QuickStroke

This project is not a medical diagnosis tool. Any clinical, commercial,
or public-health deployment requires local validation, ethical approval
where applicable, and appropriate medical supervision.

Derivative works should preserve this notice and clearly indicate that
they are based on the original QuickStroke project.
